OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few bright
OL,6,Fspells possible at first in the
OL,7,Fevening but a band of cloud and rain
OL,8,Fsoon spreads northeast, rain
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy. This clears to
OL,10,Fshowers from the west towards morning.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,13,Fsome showers, these more frequent over
OL,14,Fthe southwest in the morning, the best
OL,15,Fof the drier weather towards eastern
OL,16,FBorders.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
