OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloud,
OL,6,Frain pushes northeast Saturday, heavy
OL,7,Fat times later. A band of rain pushes
OL,8,Fsoutheast Sunday, heavy for a time.
OL,9,FRain clears Monday morning, then
OL,10,Fbright spells and some showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
